      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIVERGENCE (6) quickly into stride to win over the 342m at this track two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Can find winning form. PAW SHAYNA (7) scored two back in the quickest time on the program then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 11 length 4th at Murray Bridge (30.77). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Can figure in the finish. JUBILANT (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (31.22) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from three starts. One of the main contenders. BONMATI (8) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.",
